        <li><span style='color:#087b08'><strong>APERS Bounding Mine</strong></span> - Pressure activated anti-personnel mine (Bouncing Betty). Initial charge propells the main charge into the air which will explode mid air above ground spreading shrapnel over a large area.</li>
