        <img src="/wiki/images/MortarCard.png" title="MortarCard.png" width="300" alt="MortarCard.png" /><figcaption aria-hidden="true">MortarCard.png</figcaption>
    </figure>
    <p><span style='color:#087b08'><strong>Step 4: Aim &amp; Fire</strong></span></p>
    <p>Set Charge, Elevation (in Mils) and Direction (in Mils) to align your Mortar with the Target and Fire. Communicate your status to the other units:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Rounds Away - First Round fired at Target.</li>
        <li>Rounds Complete - Last Round fired at Target.</li>
        <li>Splash Out - 7s warning before first impact.</li>
    </ul>
